Difficulties are already starting to appear. I will probably have a lot of trouble getting a medical certificate, due to the FAA's stance on certain medications.
Not impossible, but it's going to take ENORMOUSLY amount of time and require A LOT of extra work.
Even though it's discouraging, it's just another problem to solve, and for now, it seems *completely* surmountable. It's just that it's going to take a lot of time and $$.
In case the challenge that awaits me interests you.
The FAA is not a fan of ADHD. It does not issue a medical certificate if you are undergoing treatment for it.
